{
  "id": "s1_crepa",
  "audio_theme": "ritorno_casa_hum",
  "stat_entry": [
    {
      "stat": "segreto",
      "op": "lte",
      "value": 10,
      "goto_branch": "intro_precaria",
      "prepend": true
    }
  ],
  "pages": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cr_p0_a",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "mallow"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cr_p0_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Deep night. The kitchen is dark. Only the fridge light when Mallow opens the door and stops."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p0_a_t2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He's holding something. A piece of cloth. The burned shirt — the one Favilla hid at the bottom of her backpack and said she threw away."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p0_a_t3",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "I found it this morning. While looking for Lex's charger."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p0_a_t4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "I wasn't trying to snoop. But it was in my hand. And I didn't know what to do with it."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p0_a_t5",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He's not angry. It's worse. He's hurt."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_4.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cr_p1_a",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "mallow",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cr_p1_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Favilla feels her hands heating up. She hides them behind her back. The gesture doesn't escape Mallow."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p1_a_t2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "I don't want to fight. I just want... to understand. But if you don't want to tell me anything, at least tell me why you can't tell me."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p1_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "From the playpen, a rustle. Lex is awake."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p1_a_t4",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He doesn't cry. He doesn't laugh. He watches. And for the first time, Favilla sees something in his eyes she's never seen before: sadness."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p1_a_t5",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex wanted all of this. His plan was to reveal the truth to dad. But now, seeing mom and dad like this — facing each other, distant — he's not sure he wants it anymore."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p1_a_t6",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "Lex. You too. You know too. And you're suffering too."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cr_p2_a",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "mallow",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cr_p2_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "The air is still. Mallow waits. Lex holds his breath. Favilla's hands burn."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p2_a_t2",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "I can turn away. I can lie. I can tell him almost everything."
            },
            {
              "id": "cr_p2_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "But nothing will be the same. Whatever I choose."
            }
          ],
          "choice": {
            "id": "crepa_choice",
            "prompt": "The burned shirt is on the table. Mallow waits. Lex watches.",
            "options": [
              {
                "id": "fidati",
                "label": "\"I can't explain it. But trust me. Please.\"",
                "goto_branch": "branch_svolta",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "segreto": 10,
                  "legame": 3,
                  "resistenza": -5
                },
                "set_flags": {
